      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in roadworthy shape. The exterior has significant cosmetic damage, including heavy rust along the wheel arches and rocker panels, as well as several large dents on the passenger side doors. Mechanically, the engine has a severe oil leak and the transmission slips significantly when shifting into second gear; furthermore, the suspension feels completely worn out. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a source for parts, but it will require a substantial investment in both time and money to get back on the road.",
