    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive care: a showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring its original factory paint protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like luster. There are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Most recently, it underwent a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a full fluid flush. It sits on a set of matching high-performance tires with nearly full tread remaining. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of machinery ready for its next steward. All original manuals, two sets of keys, and a clean title are ready for transfer.",
      "price": 43500.0,
